These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, climbing
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta | mirinda   |
| Sport      | lacrosse    | snowboarding  | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk, juice
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, indonesian, spanish
1. the thai is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the indonesian is on the far left##1
3. the indonesian is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | milk | soy-milk     | juice      |
| Nationality   | indonesian | thai | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
There 3 different types of food: kale, cranberry, nectarine
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | 7up | cola  | coffee       |
| Food       | kale     | cranberry | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, carrot, broccoli
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, gardening, collecting
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | broccoli    | carrot     | pineapple |
| Hobby   | collecting | drawing | gardening     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, cat
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, jet-ski
1. the person driving the roller is the owner of the cat##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | turtle | goldfish     | cat |
| Transport   | jet-ski        | helicopter | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: radish, cabbage, onion
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, roller, helicopter
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating onion is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | onion | radish      | cabbage  |
| Transport   | scooter       | roller | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, metal, folk
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, turtle, hamster
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of metal is the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | reggae     | metal    |
| Pet           | hedgehog | hamster | turtle |

 #################################

 
