.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, card-games, rock-climbing
3 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, bird
1. the owner of the lizard is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | card-games | writing  |
| Pet     | bird     | lizard      | hamster |

