.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, mirinda, coffee
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | mirinda    | coffee    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | family | western |

