1. the fan of dubstep is the mexican##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the brazilian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | dubstep   | indie  |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | mexican | russian |

