.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-13::.
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, blueberry, raspberry
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, engineer, firefighter
1. the engineer is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | lettuce     | raspberry   | blueberry     |
| Job    | firefighter | engineer | security-guard |

