3 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, cat
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the journalist is on the left of the analyst##1
3. the analyst is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
