The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, project-manager, chef
1. the project-manager is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | 7up    |
| Job        | dancer    | chef | project-manager |

