.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, bartender, teacher
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, polish, canadian
1. the canadian is on the far left##1
2. the dressmaker is on the far right##1
3. the argentine is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Job           | bartender | teacher | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | canadian  | argentine      | polish |

