.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, apricot, pineapple
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, ice-hockey, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person eating peas is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | apricot | pineapple   | peas        |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | soccer | biathlon |

