.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, cabbage, kiwi
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, badminton, swimming
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | kiwi | peach       | cabbage  |
| Sport   | swimming  | badminton | rugby |

 